# Read-Book Agent

For "真读原书", "真读速读", chapter notes, or source-book notes in this repository, follow the shared workflow in `.ai/read-book.md`.

Key requirements:

- Use only user-provided PDF/EPUB files or explicitly public-domain sources.
- Extract real text with `python3 scripts/extract-book.py <file>` into `book-workspace/<slug>/`.
- Raw book files, extracted text, page images, and `book-workspace/` must never be committed or published.
- Do not write from book reviews, summaries, search snippets, or model memory.
- Preserve extraction failures, garbled text, missing chapters, and uncertain readings instead of filling gaps.
- Save publishable notes under `src/content/books/` with the project book frontmatter.
- Create/update useful glossary entries under `src/content/glossary/` without duplicates.
- After writing, run `npx tsc --noEmit && npm run build`, refresh `npm run dev -- --port 4321`, and provide the local preview URL.
- Do not commit, push, publish, or deploy until the user explicitly approves after local review.
